OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m black
OL,4,Chole as international students decline
OL,6,FA decline in the number of
OL,7,Finternational students at Newcastle
OL,8,FUniversity will leave a #35 million
OL,9,Fshortfall in their budget, according
OL,10,Fto an email sent to staff.
OL,12,FThe university's vice chancellor
OL,13,FProfessor Chris Day told staff that
OL,14,Fthere will be immediate cost cutting
OL,15,Fmeasures which include a freeze on
OL,16,Fchanges to existing contracts,
OL,17,Fincluding requests for longer working
OL,18,Fhours.
