OL,4,Chole as international students decline
OL,6,FReviews are also underway for the
OL,7,Fannual staff pay review and academic
OL,8,Fpromotions.
OL,10,FIn the email, seen by the Local
OL,11,FDemocracy Reporting Service, Prof Day
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our aim is to protect core
OL,13,Feducation and research while
OL,14,Facknowledging that immediate cost
OL,15,Fcontrols will require difficult
OL,16,Fchoices and prioritisation".
