OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m black
OL,4,Chole as international students decline
OL,6,FHe said Newcastle University had
OL,7,Falready built in #15 million of
OL,8,F"mitigations" in its annual budget,
OL,9,Fbut must now find an additional #20m
OL,10,Fin savings to avoid a financial
OL,11,Fdeficit.
OL,13,FAccording to the email, Newcastle
OL,14,FUniversity's Executive Board has
OL,15,Fagreed to freeze recruitment to all
OL,16,Fnew and replacement "core funded"
OL,17,Fposts until further notice.
