OL,6,FExceptional cases will be considered
OL,7,Fif they are considered "business
OL,8,Fcritical" and all "capital projects",
OL,9,Fincluding buildings or equipment, will
OL,10,Fbe reviewed to consider the risks of
OL,11,Fpausing work or purchases against the
OL,12,Fcosts of completing them.
OL,14,FIt is also expected that the majority
OL,15,Fof the university's payment cards will
