OL,6,FA Newcastle University spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are in a sound financial
OL,8,Fposition but like many other
OL,9,Funiversities, we are managing the
OL,10,Fimpact of a shortfall in international
OL,11,Fstudent recruitment this year
OL,12,Fresulting in a fall in income.
OL,14,F"We are implementing cost-control
OL,15,Fmeasures which will allow us to
OL,16,Fprotect our core business and
OL,17,Fstrengthen our financial resilience."
