OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m black
OL,4,Chole as international students decline
OL,6,FAccording to Home Office figures,
OL,7,Fstudent visa applications between
OL,8,FJanuary and August this year, 278,700,
OL,9,Fwere 17% lower than in January to
OL,10,FAugust 2023.
OL,12,FThis follows government changes in
OL,13,FJanuary 2024 meaning most students are
OL,14,Fno longer allowed to bring dependents
OL,15,Fwith them.
