OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m black
OL,4,Chole as international students decline
OL,6,FIn February this year, Northumbria
OL,7,FUniversity announced it would slash
OL,8,Fits staffing budget by #12.5m. A move
OL,9,Fwhich the University claimed was also
OL,10,Fattributed to difficulty with
OL,11,Finternational recruitment as well as
OL,12,Fhigher than normal energy prices.
OL,14,FThe budget cut was dubbed a "crisis"
OL,15,Fby the university's chapter of the
OL,16,FUniversity and College Union. The fall
OL,17,Fin international student applications
OL,18,Fwas estimated to cost the university
OL,19,F#10m in lost income.
